<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Breathe Easy | Pollution Awareness</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f6f9;
      color: #333;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe, #00f2fe);
      color: white;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-in-out;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      padding: 12px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    nav a:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530569673472-307dc017a82d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=80') no-repeat center/cover;
      color: white;
      animation: zoomIn 1.5s ease;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }

    .section {
      padding: 50px 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      animation: fadeUp 1.2s ease-in-out;
    }
    .section h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #007BFF;
    }
    .section ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .section ul li {
      background: white;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .section ul li:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .quiz button {
      margin: 5px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .quiz button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      background-color: #218838;
    }

    form input, form textarea, form button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    form button {
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: none;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    form button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: white;
    }
    footer a {
      color: yellow;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes zoomIn {
      from { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0; }
      to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Breathe Easy</h1>
    <p>Raise Awareness. Reduce Pollution. Restore Earth.</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#types">Types of Pollution</a>
    <a href="#aqi">Live AQI</a>
    <a href="#tips">What You Can Do</a>
    <a href="#quiz">Quiz</a>
    <a href="#contact">Join Us</a>
    <a href="/admin">Admin</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Protect Our Planet</h1>
    <p>Learn. Act. Inspire.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="types">
    <h2>Types of Pollution</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Air Pollution:</strong> Emissions from vehicles, industries, and burning fuels.</li>
      <li><strong>Water Pollution:</strong> Waste dumping, oil spills, and industrial runoff.</li>
      <li><strong>Soil Pollution:</strong> Use of pesticides, landfills, and chemical spills.</li>
      <li><strong>Noise Pollution:</strong> Traffic, loudspeakers, construction noise.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="aqi">
    <h2>Live AQI (Air Quality Index)</h2>
    <p id="aqi-value">Loading AQI...</p>
    <script>
      fetch('https://api.waqi.info/feed/delhi/?token=demo')
        .then(res => res.json())
        .then(data => {
          const aqi = data.data.aqi;
          document.getElementById("aqi-value").innerText = `Delhi AQI: ${aqi}`;
        })
        .catch(() => {
          document.getElementById("aqi-value").innerText = "Unable to load AQI";
        });
    </script>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="tips">
    <h2>What You Can Do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Use public transport or carpool.</li>
      <li>Switch to renewable energy sources.</li>
      <li>Plant trees and support green spaces.</li>
      <li>Avoid single-use plastics.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section quiz" id="quiz">
    <h2>Pollution Awareness Quiz</h2>
    <p>Q1: What is the main cause of air pollution in cities?</p>
    <button onclick="alert('✅ Correct! Vehicles emit harmful gases.')">Vehicles</button>
    <button onclick="alert('❌ Incorrect. Trees help clean the air.')">Trees</button>
    <button onclick="alert('❌ Incorrect. Water is not the primary cause.')">Water</button>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="contact">
    <h2>Join the Movement</h2>
    <form method="POST" action="/contact" autocomplete="off">
      <label>Name:</label>
      <input type="text" name="name" required>

      <label>Email:</label>
      <input type="email" name="email" required>

      <label>Message:</label>
      <textarea name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>

      <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Breathe Easy. All Rights Reserved. | <a href="#">Back to Top</a></p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
